{% set changeEventExample %}
<z-tab-group id="change-event-tab">
    <z-tab label="tab 1">Tab 1 content</z-tab>
    <z-tab label="tab 2">Tab 2 content</z-tab>
</z-tab-group>

<p>Result: <b id="change-event-result"></b></p>

<script>
    const $tab = document.querySelector('#change-event-tab')
    const $result = document.querySelector('#change-event-result')

    $tab.addEventListener('z-change', ({ detail }) => {
        $result.innerText = detail.value
    })
</script>
{% endset %}

<div class="container">
    <h2>Tab-group & Tab</h2>

    <p><code>{{ '<z-tab-group>' | escape }}</code> is a component that displays <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> components one at a time, and adds a menu so that you can choose which one to display.</p>
    <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> is a component that wraps its content so that the <code>{{ '<z-tab-group>' | escape }}</code> can retreive it.</p>

    {{ example(template=minimalExample, about="Basic tabs") }}

    <hr>
    <h3 id="attributes">Attributes</h3>

    <h4 id="attributes-vertical">Vertical (z-tab-group)</h4>

    <p>The <b>vertical</b> attribute changes the layout of the tabs menu by putting it to the left instead of the top of the tab group.</p>

    {{ example(template=verticalExample, about="Vertical tabs menu") }}

    <h4 id="attributes-centered">Centered (z-tab-group)</h4>

    <p>The <b>centered</b> attribute changes the layout of the tabs menu by making it centered (horizontaly or verticaly)</p>

    {{ example(template=centeredExample, about="Centered tab menu") }}

    <h4 id="attributes-label">Label (z-tab)</h4>

    <p>The <b>label</b> attribute is used to build the menu and provides a clickable button to show the corresponding tab.</p>

    <hr>
    <h3 id="accessibility">Accessibility</h3>

    <h4 id="accessibility-tab-group">Tab group</h4>

    <p>The <code>{{ '<z-tab-group>' | escape }}</code> component is a wrapper for a list of <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> components.</p>
    <p>It displays a list of buttons meant to activate its corresponding <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> component and the content of that <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> component.</p>
    <p>Only the currently active tab button can be focused.</p>
    <p>To activate the other <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> components, you have to have focus on one of the tabs buttons and:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Use <code class="keyboard">Up</code> or <code class="keyboard">Left</code> key for <b>previous</b> tab.</li>
        <li>Use <code class="keyboard">Right</code> or <code class="keyboard">Down</code> key for <b>next</b> tab.</li>
        <li>Use <code class="keyboard">PageUp</code> key for first tab.</li>
        <li>Use <code class="keyboard">PageDown</code> key for last tab.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h4 id="accessibility-tab">Tab group</h4>

    <p>The <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> component is a wrapper for the content you want to display when this component is the one activated.</p>
    <p>When activated, the content of a <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> component should be the only one visible inside the <code>{{ '<z-tab-group>' | escape }}</code> component.</p>

    <hr>
    <h3 id="events">Events</h3>

    <h4 id="events-change-tab-group">z-change (z-tab-group)</h4>
    <p>The <b>z-change</b> event is fired whenever the active <code>{{ '<z-tab>' | escape }}</code> component changes. It is a <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/CustomEvent">CustomEvent</a>.</p>
    <p>This event provides a <b>detail</b> object containing the value of the newly active tab.</p>

    {{ example(template=changeEventExample, about="z-change event") }}
    
    <h4 id="events-change-tab">z-change (z-tab)</h4>

    <p>The <b>z-change</b> event is fired whenever the <b>active </b> of the tab changes. It is a <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent/CustomEvent">CustomEvent</a>.</p>
    <p>This event provides a <b>detail</b> object containing the new value of the tab <b>active</b> internal property.</p>
    <div class="notif">This event is used by the <code>{{ '<z-tab-group>' | escape }}</code> component. It is most likely not usefull otherwise...</div>
</div>
